 Cunha</strong><br /><strong>Coordenadora Pedag&oacute;gica</strong></p>','1','8','0','20','2006-08-11 13:41:26','68','','2008-03-26 17:01:20','68','0','0000-00-00 00:00:00','2006-08-11 13:38:34','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','','pageclass_sfx=\nback_button=\nitem_title=1\nlink_titles=\nintrotext=1\nsection=0\nsection_link=0\ncategory=0\ncategory_link=0\nrating=\nauthor=\ncreatedate=\nmodifydate=\npdf=\nprint=\nemail=\nkeyref=\ndocbook_type=','4','0','2','','','0','828','proposta-pedaga');
