font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&middot;</font></span><span><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Comic Sans MS&#39;\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">Dia e noite </font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; direction: ltr; font-family: Symbol; unicode-bidi: embed\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&middot;</font></span><span><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Comic Sans MS&#39;\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">C&eacute;u<span>&nbsp; </span>e terra </font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; direction: ltr; font-family: Symbol; unicode-bidi: embed\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&middot;</font></span><span><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Comic Sans MS&#39;\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">Terra e mar</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; direction: ltr; font-family: Symbol; unicode-bidi: embed\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&middot;</font></span><span><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Comic Sans MS&#39;\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">Frutas/&Aacute;rvores frut&iacute;feras/verduras/ervas...</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; direction: ltr; font-family: Symbol; unicode-bidi: embed\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&middot;</font></span><span><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Comic Sans MS&#39;\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">Dias, meses, anos (calend&aacute;rio, anivers&aacute;rios)</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; direction: ltr; font-family: Symbol; unicode-bidi: embed\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&middot;</font></span><span><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&nbsp;</font></span><sp