\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; direction: ltr; font-family: Symbol; unicode-bidi: embed\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&middot;</font></span><span><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Comic Sans MS&#39;\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">Animais em extin&ccedil;&atilde;o</font></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; direction: ltr; font-family: Symbol; unicode-bidi: embed\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&middot;</font></span><span><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Comic Sans MS&#39;\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">Meio ambiente: como j&aacute; sabemos, Deus criou o mundo. Mas o que est&aacute; acontecendo com ele? O que podemos fazer para n&atilde;o destruir o mundo perfeito que Deus criou?</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 7.05pt; text-indent: -7.05pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; direction: ltr; font-family: Symbol; unicode-bidi: embed\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&middot;</font></span><span style=\"width: 2.5pt\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Comic Sans MS&#39;\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">Polui&ccedil;&atilde;o &ndash; ar, &aacute;gua </font></span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 7.05pt; text-indent: -7.05pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; direction: ltr; font-family: Symbol; unicode-bidi: embed\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&middot;</font></span><span style=\"width: 2.5pt\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Comic Sans MS&#39;\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">Lixo &ndash; reciclagem </font></span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 7.05pt; text-indent: -7.05pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; direction: ltr; font-family: Symbol; unicode-bidi: embed\"><font face=\"Arial\" size